# LeakSanitizer suppressions.
#
# Our own code must be leak-free. Entries here are ONLY for known third-party
# leaks — never suppress a leak in Source/.
#
# The audio-device fallback test opens a real audio device; the ALSA and
# PipeWire (SPA) backends leak one-time internal state on device open. These are
# outside our control and unrelated to VA Synth's correctness.
leak:libasound
leak:libspa
leak:snd_pcm
